prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a funny birthday scene for Lao Lao, featuring cartoon characters that highly resemble the people in the reference photo. The scene is set against a soft, light-colored watercolor wash background with subtle paper texture and artistic paint bleeds. In the center, the older woman (Lao Lao) is depicted as a cartoon character, wearing her pink plaid shirt and grey pants, seated majestically on a ridiculously oversized, ornate golden throne. She has a playful, queenly expression, holding a bubble tea in one hand and a mahjong tile in the other. The younger woman, in her blue patterned shirt and white shorts, and the young man, in his blue button-up shirt and khaki shorts, are depicted as loyal, comical subjects. The woman is fanning Lao Lao with a giant banana leaf, and the man is presenting her with a huge, beautifully wrapped gift box, both with exaggerated, cheerful expressions. The entire illustration has a vibrant, lighthearted feel with soft, flowing colors and visible brush strokes characteristic of watercolor art. In the center of the card, positioned safely away from the edges, is the text "Happy Birthday, Queen Lao Lao!" written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script in a dark, complementary color.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
